window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>UTV founder and pioneer of the media industry Ronnie Screwvala is one of India’s most successful first-generation entrepreneurs. An avid philanthropist, he has penned <i>Dream with Your Eyes Open: An Entrepreneurial Journey</i> as one of the most inspiring entrepreneurial self-help books. Pictured relaxed and content on the cover page of the book, Screwvala provides a relentless pursuit of entrepreneurial glory and describes how others can learn from the same.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The book - an insider’s account of what it takes to start, build and scale businesses in India - details Screwvala’s vast entrepreneurial experiences gathered over 20 years of building amazing and not so amazing businesses. The book is aimed at bringing clarity to the way business setup is changing. It presents a significant account on what role entrepreneurs will play in the future of India.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The book is filled with incidents, thoughts and behind-the-scenes anecdotes of Screwvala’s career that will help young business-oriented minds to gain more knowledgeable insight into the ins and outs of entrepreneurship. Through <i>Dream with Your Eyes Open</i>, Screwvala has presented listeners with a fighting chance to make dreams come true.</p>"; 
